PrintingHeaders Property

Requires: Base Development System

Class: VI Properties (ActiveX)

If TRUE, LabVIEW prints headers for the VI. Use the PrintHeader properties in this class to customize the contents of the headers.

This property is similar to the Print header (name, date, page number) checkbox on the Print Options page of the LabVIEW VI Properties dialog box.

Syntax

object.PrintingHeaders

Data Type

Boolean
